HEADWORD: antagonists
<hw>antagonists</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>muscles having
opposite effects; the contraction of one neutralizes the contraction of
the other.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> antagonistic muscles.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

